        public Car updateCar​(UpdateCar car,
                     java.lang.Long id)
        Function update existing car object. In case we provide id, service will be searching database by id in other case object will be fetched by vin number. If you want update vin number you need to use id parameter.
        Parameters:
        car - object with updated value
        id - id of object, is not required.
        Returns:
        return updated object
